{"tid":2111173,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[議事論事] - 逢星期四晚上8時於港台電視31播出","createTime":"2020-07-16T11:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T13:34:15.000Z","uid":30,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8494170610dafbacd043334049b452dbc21b389c","tid":2111173,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:09:23.000Z","msg":"16/07/2020<br />\n<br />\n選戰起動；「見薇知著」嘉賓：蔡堅（香港醫學會會長）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/legco_review/originals/mfile_866_594024_1_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Flegco_review%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_866_594024_1_l.jpg&h=ea65ccc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/legco_review/originals/mfile_866_594024_2_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Flegco_review%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_866_594024_2_l.jpg&h=015277c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/legco_review/originals/mfile_866_594024_3_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Flegco_review%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_866_594024_3_l.jpg&h=ee901cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/legco_review/originals/mfile_866_594024_5_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Flegco_review%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_866_594024_5_l.jpg&h=e38e6cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/legco_review/originals/mfile_866_594024_9_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Flegco_review%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_866_594024_9_l.jpg&h=f9b28c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主派立法會初選結果塵埃落定，年輕社運領袖及被視為本土派的候選人獲較多支持者投票，反而部分具知名度的傳統民主派人士落選。在逾60萬人投票的情況下，初選結果對民主派陣營帶來甚麼啟示？港澳辦及中聯辦嚴厲譴責今次初選活動，是對特區選舉的非法操控，即使民主派能協調出線人選，又會否有被當局取消參選資格的隱憂？另一方面，建制派亦積極為今次立法會選舉作部署，面對民主派「35+」攻勢下，他們將會如何應戰？<br />\n<br />\n（編導：鄔永翹、張靜文）<br />\n（策劃：劉振瑛）"},{"pid":"ec4cdc95103f1e6e4c9afe6c9f553559786feb69","tid":2111173,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197ecf301af988a7de7fb68f260a16af2be9afd0","tid":2111173,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:23:56.000Z","msg":"睇緊"},{"pid":"d1627cbe8da3a73729f95a501f1d89b500c55596","tid":2111173,"uid":119408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:24:58.000Z","msg":"蔡醫生畀大量藍蛆投訴<br />\n唔認黃都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e8bfbb6a3cef508dcbaf53954d25069d8faa55","tid":2111173,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1627cbe8da3a73729f95a501f1d89b500c55596","tid":2111173,"uid":119408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:24:58.000Z","msg":"蔡醫生畀大量藍蛆投訴<br />\n唔認黃都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:42:20.000Z","msg":"勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0902e9fac973b95e399eb888a4a889e2d910cbd7","tid":2111173,"uid":256059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a3b3fa5c904238058ac403831e562ae0746b11","tid":2111173,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"我睇到好緊張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce47fb8c65f9